{
  "stem": "214.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But another thing was, when I was at the Siedlce-- that man had a business.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I think yeah, he had-- that's what he did also before-- before the war, house paint.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he was-- we're we're talking about, you know, what I'm doing, what we are doing in, what my parents are doing, and how do we live, and that whole thing.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he says, you know, if you could-- of course, you know the Jewish business, he couldn't-- he didn't have anything.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But he said, if you could-- I have a few customers, or-- or-- not customers, but people from whom he was buying in the Warsaw ghetto-- if you could smuggle to me some paint, I would pay for it.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I would pay you for it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I went back home to Skierniewice and we-- and, you know, at that time things were-- you were getting poorer and poorer and we were buying [SIGHS] potatoes.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I remember once I went with my sister because the boys were always, you know, afraid to go.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And have you ever carried on your back 50 kilograms of potatoes?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I remember when I was walking with it, I was thinking that probably to have a baby cannot be any more pain than that.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean-- some of those thoughts come back to me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember I was so-- and my sister, poor thing, she was carrying-- and then we distribute.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And again, you sold some of it, you know, gave it to your aunt, and distributed it to some neighbors and charged for it, because everything was so precious.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And people were afraid to go out.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
